headline: Reflecting On Beverages, Alcohol and Tobacco Stocks’ Q3 Earnings: Monster (NASDAQ:MNST)
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how beverages, alcohol and tobacco stocks fared in Q3, starting with Monster (NASDAQ:MNST).
